freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Vertigo. I have benign positional vertigo. It has not flared up like this for over 5 years, but was bound to happen sometime. My eyes have been itching so i am guessing allergies affecting inner ear.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I didn't sleep well, but that happens often to me. I'm very tired, but it's from lack of sleep.
Injection site pain was only for a couple of hours during the night. Nothing today.
Tummy pain probably from too much cheese. Fine after I used the bathroom.
